data.enText: a very large African bird with a long neck and long legs, that cannot fly but can run very fast

data.chText: 逃避现实的人；不愿正视现实者
data.enText: a person who prefers to ignore problems rather than try and deal with them

tr: fast-running African flightless bird with two-toed feet
a person who refuses to face reality or recognize the truth (a reference to the popular notion that the ostrich hides from danger by burying its head in the sand)

value.def: An ostrich is a very large African bird that cannot fly.
